DEPENDENCIES
------------

+ eBox components

	+ ebox

+ Debian packages (apt-get install <package>)

	+ dhcp3-client
	+ iproute
        + vlan
	+ net-tools

+ Others

	+ a VLAN (801.q) enabled Linux kernel

INSTALLATION
------------

- Once all dependencies are satisfied, type:
	
	./configure
	make install

  configure will autodetect eBox base path to install

- You can import your current network configuration into eBox
 
  $prefix/ebox-network/ebox-netcfg-import
